body.description: This upgraded J-3 still is an easy build and a great starting point for a relatively new pilot looking for their first traditional kit. Traditional builders of kits will appreciate this semi-scale Cub. Cheap to get in the air and fun to build, this J-3 is a great size model with most of the hard work is already done for you.
